'''Duos'tine''' was a famed [[Artist/Legends|artist]] from [[Loretto]]. [[Xizor/Legends|Xizor]] once ordered Duos'tine to carve a bust of him. The bust later ended up in the hands of [[Dequc]] on [[Qiaxx]] where [[Mara Jade Skywalker|Mara Jade]] hid her [[Lightsaber/Legends|lightsaber]] within it.<ref name="Mara Jade 6">[[Mara Jade – By the Emperor's Hand 6|''Mara Jade – By the Emperor's Hand'' 6]]</ref>

